    "description": "自从 2019 年我第一次玩《杀戮尖塔》以来，我就一直梦想着创建自己的卡组游戏。在《陷阱大师》中，你将作为一个年轻的忍者，构筑一套独特的“陷阱+技能”卡组，收集宝藏获取惊喜效果，每场战斗守卫不同的基地，直到准备好迎战无情的Boss。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/7e400483e4f1b0243d1cadbfbcb3cb04.avif?t=1739172992\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>对抗40多种敌人，守护100多个基地。射击、灼烧、切割、拳击、穿刺、下毒。将怪物弹入水中，或者召唤勇士替你作战。超多陷阱和技能供你消灭一波又一波的敌人！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/441f6bf3f17dd4f0ad7a7a92c1f0c0ff.poster.avif?t=1739172992\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/441f6bf3f17dd4f0ad7a7a92c1f0c0ff.webm?t=1739172992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/441f6bf3f17dd4f0ad7a7a92c1f0c0ff.mp4?t=1739172992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/14ff48ffe0a77ed68d26a70132d9e883.avif?t=1739172992\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>从最基本的陷阱卡牌开始，在旅途中收集卡牌，扩展成一个坚不可摧的多功能卡组，灵活地在不同地形上防御来自空中或地面的敌人。100多种陷阱和技能之间可以达成强大的协同，快去探索你的流派策略吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/11e3bb8ee2fd4b221e59e7e87efcec0f.poster.avif?t=1739172992\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/11e3bb8ee2fd4b221e59e7e87efcec0f.webm?t=1739172992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/11e3bb8ee2fd4b221e59e7e87efcec0f.mp4?t=1739172992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/a0c3fe0c3d611de5394e87f95da7248a.avif?t=1739172992\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>每局游戏都新鲜随机，遭遇改变你策略或旅程的奇妙事件。揭开怪物攻势背后的秘密动机，研究成为“陷阱大师”的秘籍！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/7850960c01f303517002926028cce221.poster.avif?t=1739172992\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/7850960c01f303517002926028cce221.webm?t=1739172992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330870/extras/7850960c01f303517002926028cce221.mp4?t=1739172992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br>- <strong>100多种致命陷阱和技能</strong>，构筑属于你的卡组<br>- 卡牌升级和铭刻系统，强化卡牌<br>- 防御<strong>100多个设计巧妙的基地</strong><br>- 挑战<strong>45种属性各异的敌人</strong><br>- 解锁宝藏系统，获得惊喜效果<br>- 肉鸽旅程，每次游戏都新奇刺激<br>- 神秘感十足的美术风格，身临其境的冒险体验",
